# Note: docs/archive/plans/ historical snapshot is TRACKED (history preserved per git mv).
#       CLAUDE.md mandates SOLL tools for active plans (CPT-AXO-024); markdown plans
#       here pre-date the policy. No new active plans should land in docs/plans/
#       unless re-introduced via explicit SOLL DEC. Use `soll_work_plan` / `soll_apply_plan`.

# REQ-AXO-901801 (MIL-AXO-028 cat A) — dashboard scaffolding turds. The
# Phoenix `mix phx.new` blueprint provisioned an ecto_sqlite3 Repo we
# never activated ; the .db files were created by an early experiment
# and never cleaned. Now ignored so any rebuild stays out of git ; the
# files themselves are removed by their owning commit.
src/dashboard/axon_nexus.db
src/dashboard/axon_nexus.db-shm
src/dashboard/axon_nexus.db-wal
